== 作用机制 ==
草甘膦主要是阻碍[[芳香性|芳香]][[氨基酸|氨基酸]]的生物合成，即[[苯丙氨酸|苯丙氨酸]]、[[色氨酸|色氨酸]]及[[酪氨酸|酪氨酸]]通过[[莽草酸途径|莽草酸途径]]的合成。它对EPSPS合酶（5-烯醇丙酮酸莽草酸-3-磷酸合酶, 5-enolpyruvylshikimate-3-phosphate synthase）有抑制作用，该酶可以催化莽草酸-3-磷酸(shikimate-3-phosphate, S3P)和磷酸烯醇式丙酮酸(phosphoenolpyruvate)向5-烯醇丙酮酸莽草酸-3-磷酸(5-enolpyruvyl-shikimate-3-phosphate, EPSP)的转化，因此草甘膦干扰这一生物合成的酶促反应，导致[[莽草酸|莽草酸]](shikimate)在生物体内的积累。抑制酶使莽草酸在植物組織積累並轉移其他生化過程的精力和資源。雖然幾小時內植物停止增長，需要幾天時間樹葉開始變黃。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=E. Schönbrunn ''et al.''|title=Interaction of the herbicide glyphosate with its target enzyme 5-enolpyruvylshikimate 3-phosphate synthase in atomic detail|journal=PNAS|year=2001|volume=98|pages=1376–1380|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/98/4/1376?ijkey=1b1ce735beee08811872889841023d179742ef2c|issue=4|access-date=2009-08-23|archive-date=2008-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080606065758/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/98/4/1376?ijkey=1b1ce735beee08811872889841023d179742ef2c|dead-url=no}}</ref> 此外草甘膦也可以抑制其他植物酶<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Su, L. Y. ''et al.''|year=1992|title=The relationship of glyphosate treatment to sugar metabolism in sugarcane: New physiological insights|journal=J. Plant Physiol.|volume=140|pages=168–173}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|author=Lamb, D. C. ''et al.''|year=1998|title=Glyphosate is an inhibitor of plant cytochrome P450: Functional expression of Thlaspi arvensae cytochrome P45071B1/ reductase fusion protein in Escherichia coli|journal=Biochem. Biophys. Res. Comm|volume=244|issue=1|pages=110–114|doi=10.1006/bbrc.1997.7988}}</ref>和动物酶<ref>{{cite journal en|author=Hietanen, E., K. Linnainmaa, and H. Vainio|year=1983|title=Effects of phenoxyherbicides and glyphosate on the hepatic and intestinal biotransformation activities in the rat|journal=Acta Pharm. et Toxicol.|volume=53|issue=2|pages=103–112|doi=10.1111/j.1600-0773.1983.tb01876.x}}</ref>的活性。

